# Files/dirs to copy from the main checkout into a fresh git worktree via tools
# such as Claude Code or Worktrunk.
#
# Worktrees start with only git-tracked files. This list covers gitignored
# but useful outputs that should be carried over.
#
# Keep this list small: heavy build caches such as target/ and app/build/ are
# intentionally excluded. They are shared across worktrees via sccache for Cargo
# and the Gradle build cache.
#
# Gitignore-style: one glob per line, # comments, blank-line grouping.

# App + web icons — regenerated by `just _gen-icons` (scripts/gen-icons.sh) only when
# assets/app-icon.png is newer; copying the built outputs lets that check skip regeneration.
src-tauri/icons/
public/icon-*.png
src-tauri/gen/android/app/src/main/res/mipmap-*/
src-tauri/gen/android/app/src/main/res/values/ic_launcher_background.xml
